These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, tea
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, vegafina
1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | tea  | juice |
| Cigar       | davidoff | vegafina |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
City: colone, new-york
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| City   | colone | new-york |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, western
House: modern, wooden
1. the modern house is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the modern house is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | western  |
| House   | modern | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
