There are 2 different nationalities: american, australian
1. the australian is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
2. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Color   | apricot    | chestnut    |
| Nationality   | american | australian |

